"Il pulsante <computeroutput>forza pianoforte</computeroutput> crea 2 "
"pentagrammi per spartito."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button <computeroutput>sort instruments</computeroutput> is useful for "
"MIDI files where all or many instruments are placed in one track. For "
"example, in following MIDI file a piano and a flute appear in the same track:"
