#~ "(<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"../docimages/"
#~ "tie_button.png\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>) during note "
#~ "insertion. Press it after you have inserted a series of notes. Then "
#~ "select all note pairs to be tied with left mouse button."
